# rosetta-frida pre-commit hook — fast, scoped.
#
# Runs `lint-staged` which fixes ESLint issues + Prettier formatting on
# JUST the files you've staged. Typically completes in ~1-2 s.
#
# Coverage / typecheck / repo-wide lint run at pre-push time (see
# .husky/pre-push) so the slow checks still gate before code leaves
# your machine.
#
# Bypass with `git commit --no-verify` for WIP commits.
npx lint-staged
